property.name: text
property.value: The federate "Aircraft" provides the Angle of Attack alpha and the pitch rate to federate "AutoPilot" (controller). The sensors and the actuator are represented in the AircraftSAct model.

property.name: text
property.value:
This model is based on the F-14 Longitudinal Flight Control model (f14.mdl) from Matlab. The composite actorPilotGForce uses the d/dt actor (derivative).
The pilot g force indicates the stresses on the aircraft (that can be destructive).
